      "span_text": "Under this unified approach, the systematic relation between the stressed and unstressed counterparts is that of a complementary preference within a suitable subset of the domain. [CITATION_1] develops a theory of focus interpretation in terms of restricted alternative semantics, where the focus semantics introduces a presupposed constraint using a focus interpretation operator ∼.",
